"Suspend me in disbelief 是英语中的一个短语，通常被用来形容人们在听或看一些超出他们正常经验或现实世界的事物时，暂时相信或接受它，尽管可能没有科学依据或合理的解释。这通常指的是人们在面对奇幻、科幻或超自然现象时产生的一种心态。 [[additional info source: various, including popular science fiction and fantasy literature, as well as online fan discussions and forums]] \[
\text{Suspend in disbelief}
\] [[context: When engaging with media, from movies and books to video games, people often "suspend in disbelief" by temporarily putting aside their critical thinking and accepting elements that defy logic or scientific understanding as part of the narrative.]\] \[

